---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Low Income Equipment 2026 - Possible',
  slug: 'low-income-equipment-2026-possible',
  excerpt: 'Low income equipment financing 2026. Equipment loans possible with lower income verification.',
  date: '2026-01-07',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 3,
  category: 'Equipment Financing',
  image: '/images/blog/low-income.jpg'
};

const keywords = ["machinery-financing","low-income","income-based"],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Equipment Financing</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

# Low Income Equipment 2026 - Possible

Lower income but need equipment? Equipment financing still possible with income-based approval in 2026.

## Low Income Equipment Options

**Still Approved If:**
- Equipment generates income
- Business viable
- Repayment realistic
- Down payment available
- **50-60% approval rate**

## 2026 Low Income Solutions

**Flexible Approvals:**

**Option 1: Lower Equipment Cost**
- RM 30k-80k equipment
- Forklifts, small machines
- **Higher approval**

**Option 2: Longer Term**
- 6-7 years instead of 5
- Lower monthly payment
- **More affordable**

**Option 3: Used Equipment**
- 30-50% cheaper
- Still reliable
- **Lower loan amount**

## Low Income Interest

| Income Level | Rate | Down Payment |
|-------------|------|--------------|
| **Moderate** | 5.0-5.5% | 0-10% |
| **Low** | 5.5-6.5% | 10-20% |
| **Very Low** | 6.5-7.5% | 20-30% |

## Get Low Income Equipment

Lower income but need equipment? Apply for income-based equipment financing.

---

**No income proof?** See [No EPF Equipment](/blog/no-epf-equipment-2026-income-based).

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton href="/en/contact">Apply for Equipment Financing</CTAButton>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>